Package org.pepstock.charba.client.resources

Interface DeferredResources.DeferredResourcesResource

  • All Superinterfaces:
    com.google.gwt.resources.client.ClientBundle, DeferredResourcesBundle
    Enclosing class:
    DeferredResources
    static interface DeferredResources.DeferredResourcesResource
extends DeferredResourcesBundle
    Client bundle to reference CHART.JS, always needed to CHARBA.
    This resources type will load the CHART.JS module in asynchronous mode in order to optimize the performance when GWT code splitting is implemented.
    Author:
    Andrea "Stock" Stocchero
